Battle of the Titans. Our hottest, sexiest Welterweights go head to head.
Adrianna is back for her first season six match up. This is the first time she has faced an opponent her size. Look for Adrianna to dominate with her size and strength.
Holly is ranked 7th this season, she has experience on her side with 10 matches under her belt. She hopes strategy and quickness will help her win this tough match up.
title: Hollie Stevens "The Amazon" (1-0)
